---

<div class="bg-forest-800 text-white overflow-hidden py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="relative lg:grid lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-8 lg:items-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl font-serif">
          What Our Campers Say
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-forest-200">
          We take pride in being a part of your family's annual tradition.
        </p>

        <dl class="mt-10 space-y-10">
          
          <div class="relative">
            <dt>
              <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center text-forest-300">
                <!-- Quote Icon -->
                <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 14.9124 16 16.017 16H19.017C19.5693 16 20.017 15.5523 20.017 15V9C20.017 8.44772 19.5693 8 19.017 8H15.017C14.4647 8 14.017 8.44772 14.017 9V11C14.017 11.5523 13.5693 12 13.017 12H12.017V5H22.017V15C22.017 18.3137 19.3307 21 16.017 21H14.017ZM5.0166 21L5.0166 18C5.0166 16.8954 5.91203 16 7.0166 16H10.0166C10.5689 16 11.0166 15.5523 11.0166 15V9C11.0166 8.44772 10.5689 8 10.0166 8H6.0166C5.46432 8 5.0166 8.44772 5.0166 9V11C5.0166 11.5523 4.56889 12 4.0166 12H3.0166V5H13.0166V15C13.0166 18.3137 10.3303 21 7.0166 21H5.0166Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="ml-12 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-cream-100 italic">"The cleanest bathhouses we've seen in 20 years of camping! The staff treated us like old friends. We'll be back every October."</p>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-2 ml-12 text-base text-forest-300">
              — Sarah T., via TripAdvisor
            </dd>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
             <dt>
              <div class="absolute flex items-center justify-center text-forest-300">
                 <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M14.017 21L14.017 18C14.017 16.8954 14.9124 16 16.017 16H19.017C19.5693 16 20.017 15.5523 20.017 15V9C20.017 8.44772 19.5693 8 19.017 8H15.017C14.4647 8 14.017 8.44772 14.017 9V11C14.017 11.5523 13.5693 12 13.017 12H12.017V5H22.017V15C22.017 18.3137 19.3307 21 16.017 21H14.017ZM5.0166 21L5.0166 18C5.0166 16.8954 5.91203 16 7.0166 16H10.0166C10.5689 16 11.0166 15.5523 11.0166 15V9C11.0166 8.44772 10.5689 8 10.0166 8H6.0166C5.46432 8 5.0166 8.44772 5.0166 9V11C5.0166 11.5523 4.56889 12 4.0166 12H3.0166V5H13.0166V15C13.0166 18.3137 10.3303 21 7.0166 21H5.0166Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
               <p class="ml-12 text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-cream-100 italic">"Perfect location for visiting the historical park. The kids loved the pool and the mining sluice!"</p>
             </dt>
             <dd class="mt-2 ml-12 text-base text-forest-300">
               — The Miller Family, Google Reviews
             </dd>
           </div>

        </dl>
      </div>

       <div class="mt-10 -mx-4 relative lg:mt-0 lg:col-start-2">
         <div class="relative space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-end justify-center h-full">
               <div class="w-full h-80 bg-forest-900 rounded-lg shadow-xl opacity-75 absolute transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4"></div>
                <!-- Using local pool image -->
                <img class="relative rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full h-80 object-cover" src="/pool_swimmin.jpg" alt="Campground Pool">
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
